:Class wss
‚ćĚ simple WebSocket server

    (‚éēIO ‚éēML)‚Üź1

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźVersion
      :Access public shared
      r‚Üź'wss' '1.2.0' '2023-12-19'
    ‚ąá

    :field public Port‚Üź22322               ‚ćĚ this port will be connected
    :field public LDRC‚Üź''                  ‚ćĚ set by the server when Conga is initialized
    :field public RootName‚Üź''              ‚ćĚ Conga root name (we maintain unique names in case you run multiple servers)
    :field public ServerName‚Üź''            ‚ćĚ server name, overrides Conga's 'SRVnnnnnnnn'
    :field public WaitTimeout‚Üź5000         ‚ćĚ how long DRC.Wait will wait before timing out
    :field public Handler‚Üź''               ‚ćĚ name of the handler function, if any
    :field public Conx‚Üź0 2‚ćī‚äā''             ‚ćĚ table of [;1] connection number, [;2] WebSocket security key
    :field public HTMLFolder‚Üź''            ‚ćĚ folder name containing HTML to be served
    :field public AppFolder‚Üź''             ‚ćĚ folder where application code and/or resources may reside
    :field public CodeLocation‚Üź''          ‚ćĚ where to look for application code (set in makeCommon, if not set by user)
    :field public DefaultPage‚Üź'index.html' ‚ćĚ name of default HTML page
    :field public ShowHTMLRenderer‚Üź1       ‚ćĚ open the HTMLRenderer interface?
    :field public Aliases‚Üź0                ‚ćĚ resource mapping - either a file name, or 2-column matrix of [;1] alias [;2] path

‚ćĚ event handlers - set to a function name to be called when the event happens
